- âœ… HTTP requests (`requests.Session`, `requests.get`)
- âœ… Whisper models (`whisper.load_model`, `whisper.transcribe`)
- âœ… File I/O (use `tempfile.TemporaryDirectory`)
- âœ… spaCy models (mock NER extraction)
